# Data Contract Rules

Read `.ai/context/data-contracts.md` before changing API routes, database schemas, env vars, package exports, or shared validators.

## Key reminders

- Refresh snapshots with `pnpm ai:contracts` after contract changes.
- Use `pnpm ai:env` to report env drift.
- Do not infer contracts from memory when `.ai/contracts/*.generated.md` exists.
